This product includes a Lean 4 formalization developed against Mathlib and
PrimeNumberTheoremAnd. Their licenses and attribution notices remain those of
their respective projects.

The initial proofs were generated and formalized in Lean using OpenAI's
GPT 5.6 Sol; the authors then verified and rewrote the proofs to improve
readability and provide additional context. The formal declarations are
checked by the Lean kernel and the release audit documented in AUDIT.md.
